Description_lang: Thimble has located hidden caches in the crevices of Azj-Kahet. Find and follow her to reap the riches inside them.

description_blz.en_US: Thimble has located hidden caches in the crevices of Azj-Kahet. Find and follow her to reap the riches inside them.
description_blz.es_MX: Dedal ha encontrado alijos ocultos en los recovecos de Azj-Kahet. Búscala y síguela para cosechar las riquezas que contienen.
description_blz.pt_BR: Aracninha encontrou baús escondidos nas fendas de Azj-Kahet. Encontre-a e vá com ela para colher suas riquezas.
description_blz.de_DE: Fingerhut hat in den Spalten von Azj-Kahet verborgene Schätze ausfindig gemacht. Findet sie und folgt ihr, um die Reichtümer einzustreichen.
description_blz.en_GB: Thimble has located hidden caches in the crevices of Azj-Kahet. Find and follow her to reap the riches inside them.
description_blz.es_ES: Dedal ha localizado alijos ocultos en las grietas de Azj'kahet. Encuéntrala y síguela para obtener las riquezas que esconden.
description_blz.fr_FR: Croquette a trouvé des caches dissimulées dans les crevasses d’Azj-Kahet. Trouvez-la et suivez-la pour récolter les trésors qu’elles contiennent.
description_blz.it_IT: Tessitino ha localizzato delle casse nascoste negli anfratti di Azj-Kahet. Trovala e seguila per razziare le ricchezze che si trovano all'interno.
description_blz.ru_RU: Наперстик нашла тайники в закоулках Аз-Кахета. Найдите ее, чтобы она отвела вас к сокровищам.
description_blz.ko_KR: 팀블이 아즈카헤트 곳곳의 틈새에서 숨겨진 보관함을 발견했습니다. 팀블을 찾아 따라가면 보관함에 숨겨진 보물을 획득할 수 있습니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 辛布爾在阿茲-卡罕特的縫隙找到了隱藏的寶箱。找到她，跟她去搜刮裡面的財寶。
description_blz.zh_CN: 顶针发现了藏在艾基-卡赫特阴暗角落里的秘藏宝物。寻找并跟随她，将其中的财富据为己有。
